    "status": "AUTO-VERIFIED — 181/181 cells public-ready as of 2026-05-15. Last auto-fetch by tw:dgpa-extras-v2.",
    "currency": "TWD",
    "notes": "Taiwan civil servants are paid via a 俸點 (pay point) system. Each 職等 (grade) and 級 (rank within grade) maps to a 俸點 value in the range 160-800, which converts to monthly salary via the statutory 公務人員俸額表 published by DGPA. Annual = monthly × 12. Lunar New Year and year-end bonuses are discretionary, not guaranteed."
  },
  "grades": [
    {
      "code": "BPT",
      "description": "俸點 (Pay Point) — Taiwan's unified pay scale. Each civil servant's rank (職等 grade × 級 step) maps to a 俸點 value from 160 (lowest entry) to 800 (top of 簡任 senior appointment). This page shows the full 俸點 → 月支數額 mapping published by DGPA. 委任 (Elementary Appointment) covers 職等 1-5; 薦任 (Recommended) covers 6-9; 簡任 (Designated) covers 10-14."
    },
    {
      "code": "EDU",
      "description": "教育人員薪額 (Education Personnel Pay) — parallel pay scale for public-school teachers, professors, and administrators under 教師待遇條例. Uses 薪額 points (90 to 770) rather than 俸點; monthly amounts match the civil-service 俸額 scale at equivalent levels."
    },
    {
      "code": "EMP",
      "description": "雇員薪額 — non-career employees with 薪點 (pay points) 140-310 across 本薪 and 年功薪 stages. Appointed per 雇員管理規則 without 職等."
    },
    {
      "code": "MGMT",
      "description": "主管職務加給 (Management supplement) — paid monthly on top of base 俸額 for civil servants in supervisory roles. Amount depends on 職等 (grade 5-14) under DGPA 附表5. Only managers receive this; non-supervisory staff do not."
    },
    {
      "code": "POL-MIN",
      "description": "政務人員 — Cabinet Minister (部長 / 相當職務). Head of a ministry."
    },
    {
      "code": "POL-YP",
      "description": "政務人員 — President of the Five-Yuan Government (四院院長). Highest political role: President of Executive/Judicial/Examination/Control Yuan."
    },
    {
      "code": "POL-YVP",
      "description": "政務人員 — Vice President of the Five-Yuan Government (四院副院長)."
    },
    {
      "code": "POLICE",
      "description": "教育警察俸點 (Education & Police pay-points) — police officers and education personnel use a parallel 俸點 numbering on the same 公務人員俸額表 (column 2). Monthly amounts are identical to the civil-service 俸點 scale at the same row."
    },
    {
      "code": "PROF",
      "description": "專業加給(二) (Professional supplement, Type II) — the standard monthly professional allowance for most civil servants and police under DGPA 附表6. Paid to every career 公務人員 on top of 俸額. Mapped by 職等 1-14."
    },
    {
      "code": "WKR",
      "description": "技工工友 — Technicians and General Workers (public sector manual/technical support) with 薪點 90-170 mapping to monthly 工餉."
    }
  ],
